\s IJAMBO RY’AGAKIZA
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ijambo ry’agakiza niyo mbuto ya Yesu kandi imitima yacu niyo mbibe abiba mo.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Nimucyo twitegure kugaruka kwa Yesu tugaragaze imbuto isa nuko yayiteye.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Iyo mbuto kuri twebwe abanyamahanga yatewe na Petero yuzuye umwuka wera. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Reba Ijambo ry’Imana mu byakozwe n’Intumwa mugice cya kabiri ugeze kuri mirongo ine n’umwe. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Bari mu cyumba kimwe kandi bahuje umutima buzuye umwuka wera ubwo bavuga indimi nshya. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Abari Yerusaremu babanyamadini barabanegura babatuka ngo basinze.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Petero arahaguruka ababwira ashize amanga ati Yesu wawundi mwishe niwe wakoz’ibi. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Ababwir’ibya Yesu abiba imbuto y’Umwami bamwe bagira ubwoba baramubaza bati. \bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Bati tugire dute kotwakoze icyaha kibi ati mwihane mubatizwe mw’ Izina rya Yesu.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Igihe cyarageze Intumwa barazica nta kindi bazihoye ni Izina rya Yesu. \bd*
\pc \bdit Iyo imbuto idapfuye hanyuma ngo imere ntishobora gukura ngo yere imbuto nyinshi kandi umubibyi nawe ntajya gusarura atarabona imbuto isa n’uko yayiteye.\bdit*
